'''Sonia Shirsat''' Sonia Shirsat ek Bharotantli Fado gavpi. Ti Goenchi, jem 1961 vorsa meren ek  Purtugez vosahot asli ani atam Bharotachem ek Rajio zavn asa.Tika  "Jogantli  Goenchea songitachi Rajdut".[1] mhonn pachartat ani tinnem sonvsar bhor, Bharotant ani chodd korun Goeantlea sonskrutik ani songitachea suvalleamni kariokrom keleat Ti 13 vegllea bhasamni gaita<ref name="GoaStreets">{{Cite web}}</ref>

== Fattbhuim ==
Survatek, Shirsat kaideant ek veakhean divpi asli. Goeantlea vortomonpotrache niall hannim nond kelam ki tinnem "ulovpache kosbent, ti vevsaik gavpi zavche poilim ek ontoraxttrio tosrip pottkailam,.".[3] Tinnem LL.M (Master's in Law) podvi melloilea..[3]Ti Ti chhond koxi gavpak lagli ani ti ek vevsaik gavpi 1999 vorsa pasun asa.[3] Tichi avoi Romi Katolk ani ticho bapui, Hindu.

== Fado-nt proves ==
Shirsat,Bharoteam thoddea modem, ekuch nhoi zalear, Fado-nt  utkruxtt, ek songitachi tora zacho sod Purtugalant 1820 vo adim sumarak asa; ektti zavn asa. Tika thoddim vorsam  fattim Goeant gitar xikoitalo,tea Purtugez gitarist Antonio Chainho haka xroi dita..Kariaxalla zalea uprant, to Fado gavpachea sodant aslo.. Shirsat-icho tallo "hea kantarak poripurnnant boslo", ani hea vorvim “ticho sumell hea torant” zalo, oxem ti sangta. Panch vorsam modekat, tinnem apli poili ekoddi kariavoll 2008 vorsa Purtugalant keli.

2016 meren,tinnem Goem, Damanv[disambiguation needed], Bangalore, Mumboi, Delhi, Kolkata, Luxembourg, Macau, Kuwait, France, Singapore, Hawaii, Nepal, Canada, London, Dubai, Muscat, Lisbon anid Qatar hanga kariakrom keleat.[1] Tinnem California,  Toronto,  Paris,  Porto,  Oeiras ani Seoul hangai kariavolli keleat.{{As of|2016}}{{dn|date=October 2018}}{{dn|date=October 2018}}

Shirsat hinnem nanvvostea jogantlea Fado gavpeam sangata dakhovnneo keleat, zantunt Katia Guerreiro, Maria Ana Bobone, Raquel Tavares, Rao Kyao, Carlos do Carmo, Argentina Santos, Miguel Capucho, Ricardo Rocha ani Mestro Antonio Chainho hancho somavex asa.[4] Tinnem sabar favtti zaiteach Purtugalant aslolea TV vahinicher kariavolli keleat, zantunt jivea dakhovnneacho somavex asa ani hem RTPI, Sociedade Independente de Comunicação andi Televisão Independente hantunt zavnk pavlam.

Goeant, tika sabar kodden jivea kariavollim khatir vollkhotat zantuntCalangute-chea Art Chamber[5] hacho somavex asat .

== Her prapteo ==
Shirsat hi ekuch vevsaik Fadista (Fado gavpi) Bharoti Upkhonddant asa, ek tora tinnem 2003 vorsa savn apnnailea. Ti kariaxallo hatalltta ani nim-xastrio torachea songit Fado hacher ulovpam korta. Purtugez Fado xivai, Shirsat-ak Paromporik ani Pop songit Goeant gavpi mhonn vollkhotat.

== Songitxastr ani dakhovnneo ==

* Agost 2016: Fado in the City dakhovnn
* 2013: Ek Konkani album Ugddas, uzvaddailo ji ek lokprio kantaranchi punji tea bhaxechi zavn asa..[6] He punjent famad songitkaranchea songitacho torzumo zoxe porim Alfred Rose, Chris Perry, Frank Fernand, Wilfy Remembus, heram sangata asa. Shirsat orxim Fado gavpa khatir gazlea, zorui ti Konknni songita khatirui halim vavurta.<br />
* Mas 2010: 'Lisgoa' albumachem vimochon zantunt Shirsat hinnem Antonio Chainho sangata kam kelam.<br />
* Mai 2010: Shirsat hinnem aplo poilo album, 'Saudades de Fado', Rock ani Raaga,hanchea sangata Goeant uzvaddaila.
* 2006: Purtugalant  Fado xixvruti khatir venchpant aili.

== Tosripam ==
Shirsat hinnem 2016 Abrilant: Boreantli Gavpi (Ostori)Tosrip[7]  Tiatr Academy of Goa koddlean melloilam.

Tika Ustad Bismilla Khan Yuva Puroskar, 2016, Paromporik Songit[8] hea vorgonnant mell’lla zo Sangeet Natak Akademi, Bharotachea Sorkarachea Sonskrut Montrailoen bhettoila. Yuva Srujan Puroskar 2011, Goenchea Sorkaran Tornnatteanchea vorgonnant soglleant vhodd tosrip sonskrutaie vibhagant  tika divpant aila.

== Prosar madheomachi protikria ==
